OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1778933513
OL,3,CBody of man who entered water at
OL,4,CRedheugh Bridge found after month-long
OL,5,Csearch
OL,7,FA body has been found in the search
OL,8,Ffor a man who entered the water at
OL,9,FRedheugh Bridge in April, police have
OL,10,Fconfirmed.
OL,12,FThe man, identified as Dean Larvin,
OL,13,F39, is reported to have entered the
OL,14,FRiver Tyne just before 10pm, on Friday
OL,15,F10 April.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
