PN,42502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1778933513
OL,3,CBody of man who entered water at
OL,4,CRedheugh Bridge found after month-long
OL,5,Csearch
OL,7,FOn Saturday 2 May, emergency services
OL,8,Fwere called to Derwenthaugh Marina in
OL,9,FBlaydon, due to a report that a body
OL,10,Fhas been discovered in the water.
OL,11,FOfficers have now confirmed that this
OL,12,Fhas been formally identified as Dean.
OL,14,FIn a tribute, his family said: "Dean
OL,15,Fwas a dearly loved son, brother,
OL,16,Fbrother-in-law, uncle and friend. He
OL,17,Fhad the kindest heart, the most
OL,18,Famazing soul, and a happy, bubbly
OL,19,Fpersonality that lit up every room.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1778933513
OL,3,CBody of man who entered water at
OL,4,CRedheugh Bridge found after month-long
OL,5,Csearch
OL,7,F"He doted on each and every one of his
OL,8,Ffamily members and was loved so very
OL,9,Fmuch by all of his nieces and nephews.
OL,10,FDean always put others before himself
OL,11,Fand, in the past, even helped save the
OL,12,Flives of others, 'if you couldn't
OL,13,Fwalk, he would carry you'.
OL,15,F"We were all so proud of him and will
OL,16,Fmiss him more than words can say. Our
OL,17,Ffamily would like to thank everyone
OL,18,Ffor their condolences and kind words
OL,19,Fduring this heart-breaking time and
OL,20,Fespecially thank the person who found
OL,21,FDean for their compassion and help.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1778933513
OL,3,CBody of man who entered water at
OL,4,CRedheugh Bridge found after month-long
OL,5,Csearch
OL,7,F"We kindly ask for privacy as we
OL,8,Fgrieve this devastating loss. A huge
OL,9,Fthanks to the marine search and
OL,10,Frescue, emergency services, and family
OL,11,Fliaison officers that have offered us
OL,12,Fsupport every step of the way."
OL,14,FDetective Inspector Ashley Loader, of
OL,15,FNorthumbria Police's Major
OL,16,FInvestigation Team said: "Our thoughts
OL,17,Fare with Dean's family and loved ones
OL,18,Ffollowing this tragic outcome.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
