OL,3,CBody of man who entered water at
OL,4,CRedheugh Bridge found after month-long
OL,5,Csearch
OL,7,F"Officers will continue to support
OL,8,Fthem, and we would ask that their
OL,9,Fprivacy is respected during this
OL,10,Fextremely difficult time."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
